<h3>Bio:</h3><!-- Character Bio Below -->
<p>
 
Alyssa's always lost deep in the pages of some book. Whether it's distressed damsel's and prince charming's or man's battle against the unconquerable fire-breathing dragon; she's always there, instead of "here on earth" with the rest of us. She prefers to be alone, rather than with stuck up blondes chasing after the star football player, or the band geeks who insist on lugging around their instruments. She's not much into the boring, small talk of her parents or younger brother either. She's a lone-wolf dreaming of the day when she can move away and spend all of her time on a novel of her own.
 
</p>
 
